    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair, functional condition and serves as a reliable daily driver. While the engine and transmission are operational and it gets you from point A to point B without issue, the car shows clear signs of its age. You can expect some minor fluid seeps, interior wear on the upholstery, and various cosmetic blemishes like small dents and paint chips on the exterior. It has been maintained well enough to stay on the road, but it is not a showroom piece. This is a solid option for someone looking for a budget-friendly, functional vehicle who doesn't mind a bit of character and some upcoming minor maintenance tasks.",
      "price": 19500.0,
